data.description: Immaculate 3 bedroom/ 2 bath home with almost 2k square feet (1,875), built in 2014. Nestled in a community with pool, parks, walking areas, club house, tennis, and centrally located from major highways. Home has no carpet, smart thermostat and doorbell stay, block construction, & extended paved back patio, perfect for entertaining. Home is move in ready... make it yours now!!!
